DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260309T180000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260309T235500
UID:3a3c407ef225216db40d8403eab32f60@cityofevanston.org
DESCRIPTION:<p>Meeting <strong>agendas </strong>are posted 48 hours in adv
 ance on the City Council <strong><a href="https://cityofevanston.civicweb.
 net/Portal/MeetingInformation.aspx?type=23" target="_blank">Meeting Portal
 </a></strong> page. A <strong>Zoom link</strong> to join the meeting virtu
 ally is included in the posted agenda.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center\;
 "><span class="btn"><a href="https://cityofevanston.civicweb.net/Portal/Me
 etingInformation.aspx?type=23" target="_blank">Visit the Meeting Portal</a
 ></span></p>\n<p>This meeting will be broadcast live on Channel 16 and rep
 layed later in the week. Watch online anytime at <a href="../residents/cit
 y_communications/city_television.php" target="_blank">cityofevanston.org/c
 hannel16</a> or on your television via Comcast (Channel 16) or AT&amp\;T U
 -Verse (Channel 99 &rarr\; Evanston &rarr\; City Channel 16).<br /><br /><
 /p>\n<h2><span style="font-size: 18px\;"><strong>Public Comment</strong></
 span></h2>\nWe welcome and encourage public participation! Members of the 
 public may:<br />\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Attend in person</strong> &mdash\; Sp
 eakers are asked to arrive early and sign up on the public comment sheet n
 ear the entrance of the meeting room.</li>\n<li><strong>Join virtually via
  Zoom</strong> &mdash\; Sign up to provide comment by completing the City 
 Clerk's online form.</li>\n<li><strong>Submit written comment</strong> &md
 ash\; Email your comments to <a href="mailto:publiccomment@cityofevanston.
 org" target="_blank">publiccomment@cityofevanston.org</a> before the meeti
 ng.</li>\n</ul>\nFor more information\, visit the <a rel="noopener nofollo
 w noreferrer" href="https://www.cityofevanston.org/government/public-comme
 nt-guide" target="_blank">Public Comment Guide</a>.<br /><br />\n<h2><span
  style="font-size: 18px\;"><strong>Accessibility &amp\; Accommodations</st
 rong></span></h2>\nThe City of Evanston is committed to making all public 
 meetings accessible to people with disabilities. To request accommodations
 \, please contact <a href="mailto:disabilityservices@cityofevanston.org" t
 arget="_blank">disabilityservices@cityofevanston.org</a>\, call <strong><a
  href="tel: 18478662919">847-866-2919</a></strong> (Voice)\, or <strong><a
  href="tel: 18478665095">847-866-5095</a></strong> (TTY). Requests must be
  made at least 48 hours in advance.
LOCATION:Lorraine H. Morton City Hall - Council Chambers (909 Davis Street
 \, 2nd Floor)
URL:https://cityofevanston.civicweb.net/Portal/MeetingInformation.aspx?typ
 e=23
X-SOURCE:City of Evanston City Council
END:VEVENT
